{"tid":1659743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不可抗力因素？關心妍深圳個唱被取消","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T16:58:26.000Z","uid":60281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c35baeb1abddeb5389f34541f2005b034f00294","tid":1659743,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"佢都有事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/娛樂/不可抗力因素？關心妍深圳個唱被取消-192811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%8A%97%E5%8A%9B%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%9F%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E5%A6%8D%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%80%8B%E5%94%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88-192811&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=77bfcbd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/娛樂/不可抗力因素？關心妍深圳個唱被取消-192811</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/10/1571291217_ae-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F10%2F1571291217_ae-1280w.jpg&h=e6562de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關心妍原定於本月26日在深圳寶安體育館舉行個唱，不過距離開騷前一星期，大會在官方微博宣布個唱取消，令不少歌迷大失所望。<br />\n<br />\n大會表示「由於不可抗力因素影響，無法如期舉行」對於個唱取消令成歌迷做成不便與困擾，他們向各方表達歉意，並已安排退票，著購票人士到購票網站或致電原購票務單位了解手續詳情。雖然大會沒有明示「不可抗力因素」是甚麼，但有歌迷表示一定與時事政治有關。同時，大會又指關心妍《TOUCHING MOMENT時刻觸動演唱會2019》將繼續於中國其他城市舉行，按照原本計劃，關心妍尚有東莞一站，但至今仍未有任何消息，而她在7月中就到廣州開騷，也是巡唱的首站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/10/1571291239_AO-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F10%2F1571291239_AO-1280w.png&h=48ad2a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於個唱突然被取消，關心妍說︰「真的很遺憾，本來為深圳站所準備的驚喜要等到下一站了。 各位歌迷朋友不要失望！未來我們還有很多機會見面，我依然期待著能看到你們在台下支持我呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/10/1571291243_AL-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F10%2F1571291243_AL-1280w.png&h=e7cedad8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"553d04e72e9a2e05109fbf977324fa58ac8fbb88","tid":1659743,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dbabb2ac6cf7f60abb70e8afa93324e78e148cf7","tid":1659743,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"係共產主義嘅鐵拳"},{"pid":"b1b702862b66570bebf0978cd9c92dff9786169d","tid":1659743,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"驚佢基督徒唱D基督教詩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"cd1345270e349e28df01c06d29033bc231051755","tid":1659743,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbabb2ac6cf7f60abb70e8afa93324e78e148cf7","tid":1659743,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"係共產主義嘅鐵拳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f865bd81607aa000457dabada1246b0146d16287","tid":1659743,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"抵。"},{"pid":"affbd2c976d075052990161539850f3710601135","tid":1659743,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"關菊英唔知得唔得"},{"pid":"45a5b052064e739cda137dc1f786686b375ecd4d","tid":1659743,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}